Interledger Core 0.9.2-SNAPSHOT API

パッケージ 
パッケージ 説明
org.interledger
The main package for top-level Interledger objects.
org.interledger.codecs
This package holds all codecs for the Interledger project, including top-level interfaces and abstract classes that can be utilized to create more specific codecs, such as for ASN.1 OER, JSON, Protobuf, and more.
org.interledger.codecs.oer  
org.interledger.codecs.oer.ilp  
org.interledger.codecs.oer.ilqp  
org.interledger.codecs.oer.ipr  
org.interledger.codecs.packettypes  
org.interledger.codecs.psk  
org.interledger.ilp
This package contains classes related to the core Interledger Protocol (ILP) which is the foundational protocol in the overall Interledger suite of protocols.
org.interledger.ilqp
This package contains classes related to the Interledger Quoting Protocol (ILQP) which is one protocol in the overall Interledger suite of protocols.
org.interledger.ipr
This package contains classes related to the Interledger Payment Request Protocol (IPR) which is one protocol in the overall Interledger suite of protocols.
org.interledger.psk
